<body>
  <h1>Tanow App – Account and Data Deletion Policy</h1>

  <h2>How to request account deletion</h2>
  <p>Send an email to <strong>tanow.app@gmail.com</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Subject: <em>Request to delete Tanow account</em></li>
    <li>Include your user ID or login email</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What data will be deleted?</h2>
  <p>Your account and all data on our servers will be permanently deleted:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Task lists</li>
    <li>Reminders</li>
    <li>Recurrence settings</li>
    <li>Preferences</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Local data on your device</h2>
  <p>Local data will be deleted when you uninstall the app from your device.</p>

  <h2>Deletion timeline</h2>
  <p>We process deletion requests within 7 business days.</p>
</body>
